text: Anrijs is a Latvian masculine given name. It is an alternative spelling of Henrijs and alternative of Indriķis, the Latvian forms of Henry. It may refer to: * Anrijs Matīss (born 1973), Latvian politician and former Minister for Transport of Latvia * Anrijs Sirmais, Latvian actor Category:Latvian masculine given names
title: Anrijs
